#. Tag: title
#: storage_multipath.xml:1125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preparing SAN Devices for Multipathing"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_multipath.xml:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before configuring multipath I/O for your SAN devices, prepare the SAN "
"devices, as necessary, by doing the following:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_multipath.xml:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure and zone the SAN with the vendor’s tools."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_multipath.xml:1137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure permissions for host LUNs on the storage arrays with the vendor’s "
"tools."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_multipath.xml:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Install the Linux HBA driver module. Upon module installation, the driver "
"automatically scans the HBA to discover any SAN devices that have "
"permissions for the host. It presents them to the host for further "
"configuration."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: storage_multipath.xml:1150
#, no-c-format
msgid "No Native Multipathing"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_multipath.xml:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that the HBA driver you are using does not have native "
"multipathing enabled."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
